data.description: Atop a mountain just outside of Orofino proper, minutes away from Dworshak Reservoir. This custom-built log cabin home boasts a fully finished main floor with artisan woodworking features, a full wrap-around porch, and a custom rock fireplace. Unfinished loft and walkout basement with two additional non-conforming bedroom spaces. Oversized shop with two bays for equipment or toys, workshop/craft room off the main home, and established garden area with chicken coop. A true Idaho gem of a home with lots of land, 48.5 acres of gently rolling terrain with several large areas of flat land including timbered acreage. Per the County, this property may also be subdivided into smaller parcels for development. Property is accessed by private drive directly off of well maintained County road. Seller has assumable mortgage through Rocket Mortgage at 3.25%.
